    <title>[TIL]2021.07.30 + 회고</title>
    <url>/2021/07/30/TIL/20210730_TIL/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="💡-오늘-한-일"><a href="#💡-오늘-한-일" class="headerlink" title="💡 오늘 한 일"></a>💡 오늘 한 일</h2><ul>
<li>Rubber Duck Debugging</li>
<li>개발 블로그 작성</li>
<li>Quiz 제작</li>
</ul>
<span id="more"></span>

<br>

<h2 id="✍🏻-회고"><a href="#✍🏻-회고" class="headerlink" title="✍🏻 회고"></a>✍🏻 회고</h2><ol>
<li><p>깃허브로 PR(Pull Request)를 처음 사용해보다보니, 어떻게 코멘트를 남겨야하는지 몰랐는데 리뷰어님이 친절하게 남겨주셨다.</p>
<p> <img src="/images/retro1.png" alt="conversation">앞으로는 conversation에 상세히 작성하도록 할게요 👍🏻</p>
</li>
<li><p>favicon 추가하기.</p>
 <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Head</span>&gt;</span></span>영역에 favicon을 추가하면 좋습니다.</span><br><span class="line">일반적으로 모든 사이트에서는 favicon이 사용되고 있습니다.</span><br><span class="line">자세한 사용방법은 아래 링크의 글을 읽어보시기 바랍니다.</span><br><span class="line">favicon외에도 <span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Head</span>&gt;</span></span>영역에 필수로 사용되는 태그들에 대한 정보가 있습니다.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p> <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/The_head_metadata_in_HTML#%EB%A7%9E%EC%B6%A4_%EC%95%84%EC%9D%B4%EC%BD%98_%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0">https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/The_head_metadata_in_HTML#맞춤_아이콘_추가하기</a></p>
<p> 내가 처음 제출했던 <code>&lt;Head&gt;</code>태그는</p>
 <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">http-equiv</span>=<span class="string">&quot;X-UA-Compatible&quot;</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">&quot;IE=edge&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;viewport&quot;</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>GitHub<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;./css/main.css&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p> 이랬었지만, 리뷰를 받고 수정하였다.</p>
 <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">http-equiv</span>=<span class="string">&quot;X-UA-Compatible&quot;</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">&quot;IE=edge&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;viewport&quot;</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>GitHub<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;./css/main.css&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;apple-touch-icon&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">sizes</span>=<span class="string">&quot;57x57&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;img/apple-icon-57x57.png&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  ...</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;icon&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;image/png&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">sizes</span>=<span class="string">&quot;16x16&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;img/favicon-16x16.png&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;msapplication-TileColor&quot;</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">&quot;#ffffff&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;msapplication-TileImage&quot;</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">&quot;img/ms-icon-144x144.png&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;theme-color&quot;</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">&quot;#ffffff&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p> 운영체제 별로 각 각의 사이즈 아이콘, favicon을 추가해주었다.</p>
</li>
<li><p>시멘틱 태그를 고려하여 <code>&lt;div&gt;</code>태그 대신 <code>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;</code>태그 구조로 변경해주기.</p>
<p> 나의 처음 제출한 코드는</p>
 <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;menu clearfix&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;menu-item&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Pull requests<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;menu-item&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Issues<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;menu-item&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Marketplace<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;menu-item&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Explore<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p> 이랬었지만, 수정해주었다.</p>
 <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">nav</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;Header-item menu&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;menu-item&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Pull requests<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;menu-item&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Issues<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;menu-item&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Marketplace<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;menu-item&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Explore<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">nav</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p>마지막 줄 개행 (newline at a end of file)</p>
 <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p> 이렇게 파일을 올렸었는데 html 밑에 개행을 넣어주라고 하셨다. 마지막에 개행을 넣어주는 이유는 <span  style="color: deepskyblue">POSIX</span> 명세가 그러하기 때문입니다. 명세에는 프로세스 환경, 파일과 디렉터리 등 다양한 개념을 규격화하고 있습니다. 마지막에 개행이 없다면 파일간의 차이를 알기 힘들기 때문이다.</p>
 <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="💡-VS-Code에서-마지막줄-개행을-자동으로-해주는-꿀팁"><a href="#💡-VS-Code에서-마지막줄-개행을-자동으로-해주는-꿀팁" class="headerlink" title="💡 VS Code에서 마지막줄 개행을 자동으로 해주는 꿀팁 !!"></a>💡 VS Code에서 마지막줄 개행을 자동으로 해주는 꿀팁 !!</h3><ul>
<li><p><code>VS Code</code>환경 설정에 들어간다.</p>
<p><img src="/images/retro2.png" alt="환경설정"></p>
</li>
<li><p>검색 창에 <code>insert final newline</code>을 작성 후 아래에 체크를 해준다.</p>
<p><img src="/images/retro3.png" alt="insert final newline"></p>
</li>
<li><p>그 후 파일을 저장하면 자동으로 마지막줄에 개행이 된다.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p><code>float</code> 대신 <code>flex</code>를 사용하기</p>
<pre><code> <figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.logo</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin-right</span>: <span class="number">5px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">float</span>: left;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: white;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

 `float` 속성은 꼭 알아둬야하지만, 현업에서는 사용하지 않는 속성이라고 한다.
 `float`를 `flex`로 고쳐보았다.

 <figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.Header</span>, <span class="selector-class">.Header-item</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">align-items</span>: center;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>: flex;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">flex-wrap</span>: nowrap;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.Header-item</span> <span class="selector-class">.logo</span> <span class="selector-tag">img</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>: inline-block;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">vertical-align</span>: middle;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</code></pre>
 <br></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="💬-느낀-점"><a href="#💬-느낀-점" class="headerlink" title="💬 느낀 점"></a>💬 느낀 점</h2><ul>
<li>여지껏 혼자서만 만들고 혼자서 보다보니 이렇게 코드리뷰를 받아본 적이 없었다. 내가 부족한 부분, 그리고 어떻게 하면 더 코드가 좋아지는 지를 배울 수 있었다.</li>
<li>학원이라는 울타리 안에 있을 때 최대한 많이 배우고 가르쳐주는 것을 많이 습득해야겠다고 생각들었다.</li>
<li>이렇게 같이 듣는 수강생 모두가 열심히 하려는 모습을 보고, 나에대해서 반성하고 더 열심히 해야겠다는 다짐을 해주게한 하루였다.</li>
<li>코드리뷰에 코멘트가 0이 되는 그날까지…!</li>
</ul>
<br>

<h2 id="📌-내일-할-일"><a href="#📌-내일-할-일" class="headerlink" title="📌 내일 할 일"></a>📌 내일 할 일</h2><ul>
